cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on a real-time object detection model, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the optimization of the model for non-GPU computers, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of portable devices such as laptops and cellphones also suggests a potential fit for multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the efficiency and speed of the model, which could also fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
